channel.title: 508 Client 508
channel.description: I need help like when u open the client and it starts loading in a 508 client how do i change the top of it to say TwistedScape Client?

item.title: 508 Client 508
item.dc:creator: @Mod_Kaii Mod Kaii
item.description:
@Mod_Kaii wrote:

Go into your client files, and on Applet_Sub1 edit, then press CTRL + F or edit > Find and search for TwistedScape, it should bring you to where it says TwistedScape Client, then just change that to whatever you want your client to be named, and re-upload!
